Package simplegaprule.models

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Intervaled
    Interface where common functions are kept for classes that contain a start and end date.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Campsite
    Model representing a Campsite with a name and id.
    CampspotEnvironment
    Model representing the whole campspot test case environment.
    GapRule
    Model representing a number of days that cannot exist as a gap between two reservations.
    Reservation
    Model representing a Reservation to a Campsite.
    Search
    Model that represents a reservation time search interval.
